---
title: Intake State Machine
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> OFF

    OFF --> INTAKING : SuperStructure sets INTAKING
    INTAKING --> OFF : SuperStructure sets OFF

    OFF --> ASSIST_SHOOTING : SuperStructure sets ASSIST_SHOOTING
    ASSIST_SHOOTING --> OFF : SuperStructure sets OFF

    INTAKING --> ASSIST_SHOOTING : SuperStructure sets ASSIST_SHOOTING
    ASSIST_SHOOTING --> INTAKING : SuperStructure sets INTAKING

    note right of OFF
        Duty cycle = 0.0
        Motor stopped
    end note

    note right of INTAKING
        Duty cycle = 0.8
        Full intake power
    end note

    note right of ASSIST_SHOOTING
        Duty cycle = 0.3
        Gentle feeding during shots
    end note
